ent-RMCFlightRecorderProp-name = FR-112 flight recorder
ent-RMCFlightRecorderProp-desc = A small red box that contains flight data from a dropship while it's on mission. Usually referred to as the black box, although this one comes in bloody red.
ent-RMCFlightRecorderColonyProp-name = CIR-60 colony information recorder
ent-RMCFlightRecorderColonyProp-desc = A small red box that records colony announcements, colonist flatlines and other key readouts. Usually refered to the black box, although this one comes in bloody red.
